{"tid":1686622,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"112柏麗大道集會不反時間1530-2100","createTime":"2019-11-01T09:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T00:23:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4290be89ce9f43975359c300cbcc44e267be5646","tid":1686622,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"POE 19012863<br />\n組織 : 無任何組織參與<br />\n日期 : 2019 年 11 月 2 日(星期六)<br />\n時間 : 下午 3 時 30 分開始至晚上 9 時正<br />\n地點 : 尖沙咀柏麗大道近彌敦道與加連威老道交界的行人路<br />\n活動性質 : 公眾集會<br />\n活動目的 : 人權民主和你 Sing<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/nono/POERN19012863C.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fnono%2FPOERN19012863C.pdf&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=74d85761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/nono/POERN19012863C.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"2a14686091150e469acb2c0228876fb5953bf17b","tid":1686622,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52a0ed3ed9227669b8577d329ccfdd884327309","tid":1686622,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"呢個係後備場？定係分九龍港島2邊搞？"},{"pid":"bc936c389c56231dabf9c7e4246b8b2875e4e677","tid":1686622,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c52a0ed3ed9227669b8577d329ccfdd884327309","tid":1686622,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"呢個係後備場？定係分九龍港島2邊搞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:30:00.000Z","msg":"&quot;112 「求援國際 堅守自治」公民活動日真正run down如下：<br />\n<br />\n- 3pm - 5pm: 到維園支持 逾100位候選人合法選舉聚會<br />\n- 3pm - 5pm: 環保方式前往 中環<br />\n- 5pm: 塞爆 中環愛丁堡廣場一帶 （美國集會已批不反）<br />\n- 5pm: 塞爆 中環遮打花園一帶 （紙鶴活動已批不反）<br />\n<br />\n而原訂到維園、添馬嘅嘉賓、器材、物質，將會移到愛丁堡廣場同遮打花園。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府唔好以為到時封鐵，阻止過海會有用。實不相瞞，我地香港人一早為 尖沙咀柏麗大道112集會拎埋 不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n假如封過海交通，尖沙咀應變計劃就會啟動。到時，香港人會移師到 尖沙咀柏麗大道 參加流水式和平集會。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1685372/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1685372/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ca39cca2f2018e519bca9366d41726c8bfbf024d","tid":1686622,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c52a0ed3ed9227669b8577d329ccfdd884327309","tid":1686622,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"呢個係後備場？定係分九龍港島2邊搞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:33:03.000Z","msg":"後備<br />\n盡量集中維園<br />\n咁先數到人頭<br />\n真係封鐵封隧道再算<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係咪都會過海 佢敢封晒陸路我游水都要游過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288e0a5f2d2ab127a4fc6af3221127a2451f41d7","tid":1686622,"uid":21282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4166134cc05d02628765979d89790654a86037b6","tid":1686622,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSO2Qd4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSO2Qd4.gif&h=b2e98198&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47234061e9c8cf8ce8b46161e5ea0d8406eafe4c","tid":1686622,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\